            Algorithmic Fairness and Opacity Working Group
           </h1>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->
        <div class="header-filter" style="background-image: url(https://afog.berkeley.edu/files/2018/04/5934337471_144662fb3f_o.jpg)">
